data.description:
Discover this charming 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom brick home that combines comfort and convenience. This well-maintained property features stainless steel appliances, refrigerated air for your comfort, and energy-efficient double pane windows.
Inside, you'll find a spacious living area, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, making meal preparation a breeze. 
With double pane windows throughout, this home not only provides energy efficiency but also reduces external noise, creating a serene living environment. The low-maintenance brick exterior ensures durability.
This home is located in a desirable area, close to schools, parks, and essential amenities. If you're seeking a cozy and efficient brick home with modern touches, this property is a must-see. Schedule your viewing today!
